This directory contains mkmntl host tool and gpt resize binary


WHAT IT DOES?
=============

It provide make mntl image host tool.
And it provide update mntl gpt resize binary.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================

It needs the following libs from AOSP:
1.  libc.so
2.  libcutils.so

HOW TO USE IT?
==============

The host tool 'mkmntl' is used to generate a image which's name is 'mntl.img' when build.

The binary  'mntl_gpt_resize' is execved before fs mount when bootip,
it would update nand gpt table before filesystem mount.


All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..
